metrics.name: dotnet.gc.collections
metrics.description: The number of garbage collections that have occurred since the process has started.

metrics.name: dotnet.process.memory.working_set
metrics.description: The number of bytes of physical memory mapped to the process context.

metrics.name: dotnet.gc.heap.total_allocated
metrics.description: The approximate number of bytes allocated on the managed GC heap since the process has started. The returned value does not include any native allocations.

metrics.name: dotnet.gc.last_collection.memory.committed_size
metrics.description: The amount of committed virtual memory in use by the .NET GC, as observed during the latest garbage collection.

metrics.name: dotnet.gc.last_collection.heap.size
metrics.description: The managed GC heap size (including fragmentation), as observed during the latest garbage collection.

metrics.name: dotnet.gc.last_collection.heap.fragmentation.size
metrics.description: The heap fragmentation, as observed during the latest garbage collection.

metrics.name: dotnet.gc.pause.time
metrics.description: The total amount of time paused in GC since the process has started.

metrics.name: dotnet.jit.compiled_il.size
metrics.description: Count of bytes of intermediate language that have been compiled since the process has started.

metrics.name: dotnet.jit.compiled_methods
metrics.description: The number of times the JIT compiler (re)compiled methods since the process has started.

metrics.name: dotnet.jit.compilation.time
metrics.description: The number of times the JIT compiler (re)compiled methods since the process has started.

metrics.name: dotnet.monitor.lock_contentions
metrics.description: The number of times there was contention when trying to acquire a monitor lock since the process has started.

metrics.name: dotnet.thread_pool.thread.count
metrics.description: The number of thread pool threads that currently exist.

metrics.name: dotnet.thread_pool.work_item.count
metrics.description: The number of work items that the thread pool has completed since the process has started.

metrics.name: dotnet.thread_pool.queue.length
metrics.description: The number of work items that are currently queued to be processed by the thread pool.

metrics.name: dotnet.timer.count
metrics.description: The number of timer instances that are currently active. An active timer is registered to tick at some point in the future and has not yet been canceled.

metrics.name: dotnet.assembly.count
metrics.description: The number of .NET assemblies that are currently loaded.

metrics.name: dotnet.exceptions
metrics.description: The number of exceptions that have been thrown in managed code.

metrics.name: dotnet.process.cpu.count
metrics.description: The number of processors available to the process.

metrics.name: dotnet.process.cpu.time
metrics.description: CPU time used by the process.
